Technical Implementation Notes

Based on these wireframes, here are key implementation details to add to your requirements:

1. Color Scheme Implementation:
   ```css
   /* Risk level colors */
   .risk-high { color: #dc2626; }    /* Red */
   .risk-medium { color: #d97706; }  /* Amber */
   .risk-low { color: #059669; }     /* Green */
   ```
2. Table Column Widths:
   Â· Wallet Address: 35%
   Â· Submitted: 25%
   Â· Risk: 15%
   Â· Days Pending: 10%
   Â· Checkbox: 5%
3. Responsive Breakpoints:
   Â· Desktop: > 1024px (table view)
   Â· Tablet: 768px-1024px (condensed table)
   Â· Mobile: < 768px (card view)

